data.text:
Below is a list all the films I’ve reviewed on this blog, with links to reviews, ordered by the year of the film’s original release. This isn’t everything I’ve seen during this time, and I’d been very sparse with my online reviews for much of 2017 and 2018, aside from the regular Criterion Sunday updates. Reviews of everything else are in capsule form on Letterboxd.

I implemented a simplified traffic-lights rating system for my reviews as of 2015, because of my general dissatisfaction with star ratings (and have now removed the star ratings from older reviews).

Green Tick Recommended (double-ticks are particularly good).

Amber Flawed, but may be worth seeing.

Red Cross Give it a miss (I hated it).
